{"word":"ἐμπρήθω","slug":"ἐμπρήθω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπρήθω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to blow up, inflate</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐμπεπρημένη ὗς</el> <i>a bloated</i> sow, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <el>ἐμπίπρημι</el>, <i>to burn</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}